<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>网易公司内部去掉「哥，姐，总」等称呼</h4>
<p>网易发布通知在内部沟通中去掉「哥」「姐」「总」等称呼，改用昵称代替。员工自 9 月 1 日起可在系统申请昵称。网易表示，昵称会伴随员工整个网易生涯。</p>
<p>网友：「这不就和阿里的花名一样么？」「不久后，估计会变成昵称 + 哥/姐/总。」「我们公司都是 Coco、Linda、Jason 这种，挺亲切的，老板也是直呼英文名。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357581" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>苹果：《好想回学校》</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362680" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chun.jpg" alt="" width="1309" height="1644" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chun.jpg 1309w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chun-360x452.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chun-768x965.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/chun-815x1024.jpg 815w" sizes="(max-width: 1309px) 100vw, 1309px" /></p>
